name: Torchecker
tagline: Keeps a database of known tor exit nodes and after you launch tor run the script to check your tor exit node status
body:
### Main Use.
When your working with multiple dockers, images etc and you need to check if tor is enabled and working use this.

### Quick configuration
Just amend the config.sh and your in business

### Authors and Contributors
OSINTM

### Support or Contact
